summary: Granting to Union Pacific Railroad Co., a Utah Corporation, Burlington Northern Inc., a Delaware Corporation, Chicago, Milwaukee, St. Paul and Pacific Railroad Co., a Wisconsin corporation, and to any one or more of them, their successors and assigns, a railway franchise over and across the westerly portions of East Marginal Way South and certain other streets from south of South Spokane St. to the south City Limits, until midnight December 31, 2000.
